WEBVTT

00:10:28.377 --> 00:10:31.510
But when the wind's at your back
and everything's going your way,

00:10:31.534 --> 00:10:33.824
all you notice is yourself

00:10:33.848 --> 00:10:36.205
and our own amazing talents.

00:10:36.229 --> 00:10:39.768
So we have to stop and think for a minute

00:10:39.792 --> 00:10:43.119
to recognize those tailwinds
helping us along.

00:10:45.122 --> 00:10:47.196
It's so easy to see
what's wrong with people

00:10:47.220 --> 00:10:48.509
who disagree with you.

00:10:49.139 --> 00:10:52.185
Some of you decided that I was an idiot
in the first two minutes,

00:10:52.209 --> 00:10:54.189
because I said inequality was harmful.

00:10:54.213 --> 00:10:55.440
(Laughter)

00:10:56.182 --> 00:10:58.879
The hard part is to recognize

00:10:58.903 --> 00:11:00.870
that if you were in a different position,